name: Yuzzum
Lore: 'Native to Endor, Yuzzum compete with Ewoks for food and resources. Possess thick, wooly coats. Hunt in packs. Have a musical language, making them excellent musicians.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Endor or to same site as a bounty hunter. Power +2 when present with an Ewok. During your control phase, if a bounty hunter or Rodian present, may search Reserve Deck, take one We Have A Prisoner into hand and reshuffle.',
